      "date": "2015-04-15 16:20:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHmm, right now, in racer test, I saw some substripe objects are being hold (after destroyed) because of it is attached to the master object. And I am not sure why the master object is being hold, needs to trace the debug log. (:()\n\nBut the point here is that\n\n1. eliminate the use case for loading striping on MDS side, since this is only needed for certain cases, like unlink, setattr.\n\n2. read EA is cheaper than lookup.\n\nAnything I missed here?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
